{"tid":2418977,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部開B站賬戶吸逾30萬粉絲 網民教路：影片太長播放量會很慘","createTime":"2021-02-23T04:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T04:17:28.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47fb7c6a4319ae842a086fba401f729c268417e6","tid":2418977,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"外交部發言人汪文斌稱，外交部發言人辦公室新媒體大家庭再添新成員，網民可透過B站及其他平台包括微信、微博、抖音、快手及微信視頻號等官方賬號，了解及關注中國外交。<br />\n<br />\n不過，外交部與B站網民似乎需要些時間磨合，有網民留言建議「B站更適合16:9的寬屏視頻和長視頻以及不帶bgm的原聲」、「還有記得加字幕」、「對， 我們好多人都是看網頁版的」、「一看就是直接把抖音的視頻複製貼過來」，也有人留言「視頻太長播放量會很慘的。」亦有人留意到，外交部片尾有「觀察者網」水印，「所以說這是外交部盜了觀察者網盜了外交部的視頻？」<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210222/Q2AJPY35BFHYVFAJQADQ3L6X7Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2g51s4OSvPvs71vASi0jVDu3JqyRVbNsMOgvrgq9ghDnbH-FmxrpZVLlI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210222%2FQ2AJPY35BFHYVFAJQADQ3L6X7Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2g51s4OSvPvs71vASi0jVDu3JqyRVbNsMOgvrgq9ghDnbH-FmxrpZVLlI&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XgweZXAU%2BhIfMqCJmwSRnXM%3D&h=9c2ddb36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210222%2FQ2AJPY35BFHYVFAJQADQ3L6X7Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2g51s4OSvPvs71vASi0jVDu3JqyRVbNsMOgvrgq9ghDnbH-FmxrpZVLlI&h=489e33a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210222/Q2AJPY35BFHYVFAJQADQ3L6X7Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2g51s4OSvPvs71vASi0jVDu3JqyRVbNsMOgvrgq9ghDnbH-FmxrpZVLlI</a>"}]}